Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.67,0:00:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…好咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.08,0:00:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬启  曾我部学姐  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初夏过得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.13,0:00:40.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有件事想告诉学姐  于是就写了这封信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.34,0:02:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  小澪？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.71,0:02:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了  一副魂不守舍的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…今天早上开始就一直感觉到一股强烈的视线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.07,0:02:25.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为小澪是名人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.92,0:02:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是被谁监视着似的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.59,0:02:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.11,0:02:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…别这样看我！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是自我意识过剩了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也能感觉到不知是从哪里看着我的视线…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.36,0:02:45.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜猜我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.51,0:02:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.39,0:02:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:03:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？感觉到谁的视线啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  我是一直都被别人狂看着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为小佐和就外表不错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.65,0:03:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「就」是什么意思啊  「就」！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:12.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说  尾行澪的犯人是小佐和？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.45,0:03:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会  如果是我的话可不会只看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:20.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  犯人是小猪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.25,0:03:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们想  小澪因为害怕小猪所以不太搭理它
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.11,0:03:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是小猪就贴上小澪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕  好可怕  好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  这帮人完全靠不住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:37.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  大家都认真地为澪学姐担心一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是被跟踪狂盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.52,0:03:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  谜团全都解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…对不起  我只是想这样做一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我说谜团解开了是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:04:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  今天的早饭吃的是炒面面包吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:02.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  确…确实是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.35,0:04:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为今天早上睡过头  就没时间慢慢吃早饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.56,0:04:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个炒面面包是打八折的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么连这个都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:18.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  这个东西粘在头发上了一天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.44,0:04:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就被大家盯着了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在偷窥什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和  她们是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们并不是什么可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是澪学姐粉丝俱乐部的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉丝俱乐部？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:44.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜…我明明已经要忘记那件事了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:49.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是来看小澪头发上粘标签的样子？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  从别的会员那里听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是粉丝的话为什么不立刻告诉她？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说告诉她比较好  但是…  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:05:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这种东西粘在头发上才像是学姐  很美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.78,0:05:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很美吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为是故意粘上去的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早就知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.85,0:05:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  都是因为我的关系  粉丝俱乐部的人才会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么和要道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但粉丝俱乐部还存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我还以为曾我部学姐毕业后就没了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾我部学姐是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.61,0:05:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  梓不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾我部学姐曾是小澪的粉丝俱乐部的会长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  自那以后已经过了那么长时间了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自那以后？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.91,0:05:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  那是在毕业典礼之前的3月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天澪也是觉得被别人盯着而感到害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不下去的我建议她去找学生会商量一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.09,0:05:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妄想也给我适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为谁都没有认真地担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就自己去找学生会商量了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:05.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉一直被谁看着？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是跟踪狂什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.41,0:06:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很难想象学校里会有可疑人物…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能有这样普通的反应让我太高兴了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻音部里到底都是什么反应啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真锅同学  在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:25.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  有客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把交接的资料拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和  她是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是学生会长曾我部惠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是「原」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多关照  秋山同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.81,0:06:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然轻音部的人不认识我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:43.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是两人的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在那之后等待着她们的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:51.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时的澪还完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要擅自加入奇怪的解说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么样的命运？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:57.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用  虽然不如轻音部的茶好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.37,0:07:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会  您太客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然会有跟踪狂  真是严重的问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真锅同学  你等会儿能把这件事告诉风纪委员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:14.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个  也不用这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.59,0:07:17.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  我们学校的学生遇上了麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想尽力帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想让我们的部长听一下这番话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:25.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但尾行澪的是什么人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是粉丝俱乐部之类的人…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜…这件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.54,0:07:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:35.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…没什么  会长您对轻音部很了解呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我的名字也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:38.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来  连轻音部开茶会的事也知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是真锅同学以前告诉我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我可没说过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是轻音部在各种意义上都很有名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:55.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我差不多该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:58.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐  你掉了什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.57,0:08:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山澪粉丝俱乐部会员证
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.22,0:08:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚在走廊上捡到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.34,0:08:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是上面写着学姐的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候我得说些什么  把气氛缓和下来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.54,0:08:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道会长就是犯人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.09,0:08:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说啥啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.01,0:08:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其…其实会长就是尾行我的犯人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.37,0:08:30.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有恶意的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就要毕业了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.38,0:08:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到无法再见到秋山同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就变得坐立不安…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:45.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被您这样说我也很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:50.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然感到很害羞…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:55.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会员号1号
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我也是粉丝俱乐部的会长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:09:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么学生会长就是犯人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在立场上这很难启齿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.57,0:09:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们就考虑为这样的曾我部学姐做些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:16.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  于是就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻音部让我们到大礼堂来  会是什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.52,0:09:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼拜什么的吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:28.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾我部学姐  恭喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.97,0:09:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐您毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们樱高轻音部将带着祝贺之意为您演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请听
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,0:09:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「软软呼呼Time」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1  2
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1  2  3  4
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…学姐  学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演奏已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.52,0:10:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未…未经允许就擅自使用大礼堂是不对的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…那也只是原则上的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.53,0:10:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次收到这种礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为纪念…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请帮我签个名！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请写上「澪炭签名」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.03,0:10:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聪慧的学姐的形象…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写了吗…「澪炭」…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会员号1号的会员证？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:43.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且上面是和的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实在那之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么真锅同学  粉丝俱乐部的会长也一起交接给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.82,0:10:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我·才·不·要·呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…这个会员证  我没能拒绝就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.08,0:11:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果因为没什么机会  一直没尽到做为会长的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和和…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天我是来拜托大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了粉丝俱乐部的会员  能开一场茶会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶会？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  这样下去也对不起学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.49,0:11:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  我们也会帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.60,0:11:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一直以来都受到和的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:24.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这么决定了  那要开场什么样的茶会？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连都…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  你们冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:27.71,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…首先是隆重入场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:29.81,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有切蛋糕也不能少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  送花和回忆相册之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.47,0:11:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,披露宴？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.41,0:11:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话搞个提问环节怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没在听…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:39.39,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}澪茶会时间表\N布置澪商品（音乐室）\N澪入场（特别服务）\N的蛋糕（该怎么办呢？）\N蜡烛服务\N澪鼻眼镜（爆笑表演？）\N提问环节\N来点幻灯片\N纪念品？\N照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就恭敬不如从命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶会的内容就交给大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就负责预定会场和联络了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来做海报
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:50.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带个特大的蛋糕来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,  你投入过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:54.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系  难得的华丽舞台～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:54.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大家的帮助下  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以应该会成为很棒的茶会  曾我部学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉越来越像样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:10.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为小澪的粉丝准备的豪华盛宴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪铅笔  小澪橡皮  小澪T恤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.28,0:12:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪巧克力  小澪开瓶器  小澪筷子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪搔痒耙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:20.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别弄出奇怪的东西来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是贴个小澪贴画而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.19,0:12:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然简单但也挺可爱的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下这个会有人觉得高兴吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧有烤饼干哦  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪饼干哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要说出「花了多少会费？」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.93,0:12:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？  讲的别人好像守财奴一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.35,0:12:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了  我们带慰问品来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.23,0:12:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别客气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.99,0:12:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是炒面面包
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:55.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连茶都备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:12:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…下手好快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:12:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们很期待茶会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:03.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打搅了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.99,0:13:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家似乎都很期待呢  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那最重要的曾我部学姐会过来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:17.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  来不了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然写了信  但学姐说因为社团旅行所以赶不回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.23,0:13:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就没什么意义了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要延后吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.29,0:13:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐说既然通知出去了  就不必特意改日程了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.15,0:13:33.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾我部学姐只是希望粉丝俱乐部能够继续发展下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要茶会能让现在的粉丝俱乐部成员觉得开心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也就满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好成熟的发言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女大学生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.96,0:13:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业成熟之后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也从澪的粉丝中毕业了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有那回事呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定只是碰巧撞上日程来不了而已啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:14:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  应该只是不想让我们太操心罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我…如果我也毕业的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否也会成为那样成熟的大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.42,0:14:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时在澪的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同走马灯般闪过一幕幕与朋友度过的美好时光…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:16.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了不要擅自加奇怪的解说！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那日程就照计划
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.78,0:14:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切按原定进行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  这是当天的流程表
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.93,0:14:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司仪就拜托小律和小唯咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:33.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于会场的布置方面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没有什么计划  但我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.48,0:14:35.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音乐教室也不好整理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.82,0:14:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要为大家做些什么才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:37.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让音乐教室显得凌乱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:40.57,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就从简做起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:43.79,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那现在来确认一下流程
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.28,0:14:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…真诚感谢大家参加第一次秋山澪粉丝俱乐部茶会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然冒昧  就请让我们来担任司仪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是田井中律
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:59.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及平泽唯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.38,0:15:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多指教！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:07.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎各位百忙中列坐到场…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:08.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊  这是结婚典礼的司仪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:10.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你来说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:15.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…人生起起落落后…突然出现了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.36,0:15:16.92,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律  那也是结婚典礼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了好多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多熟面孔啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  佐佐木同学也是会员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:18.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短剧就到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山澪粉丝俱乐部茶会现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:23.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有请今天的主角登场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山～澪～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  好帅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过穿制服好无聊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.55,0:15:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题！  还有宴会换装！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.86,0:15:40.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家今天在百忙中抽空集亏…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.78,0:15:46.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咬舌头了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那也很…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.90,0:15:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.83,0:15:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集…集会到唱…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.46,0:15:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,板垣…退助？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我们的表演犀利多了  小律
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么演讲就到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们开始切蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  有请小澪！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.31,0:16:13.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是初次的共同作业哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.17,0:16:13.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和谁的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是提供蛋糕和茶点服务
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及秋山澪本人的蜡烛服务
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐  这边也要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.32,0:16:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:39.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我们也该进入特别企划了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是秋山澪百连问答！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  顺带一提  每回答一个问题就请熄灭桌上的一个蜡烛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.43,0:16:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就开始第一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止听到过的最可怕的事是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.35,0:16:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  你在问什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二可怕的事是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.06,0:16:59.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个下一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:00.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三可怕的事是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.53,0:17:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个下一个下一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四可怕的事是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.15,0:17:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百物语？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…下一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你怕什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.53,0:17:12.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪同学～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:13.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么各位～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有什么想问的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡的话先洗哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲…莲蓬头？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扫浴室？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃鲷鱼烧喜欢先吃头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先吃鳃盖骨？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是哪里啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:30.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  让我们进入下一个环节
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将用幻灯片来回顾小澪精彩的半辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17岁就已经半辈子了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:46.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（秋山澪生活相册）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.08,0:17:53.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长大了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:18:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…比起澪学姐  律学姐你是不是更抢镜啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那是我家相册的照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.81,0:18:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的茶会终于接近尾声了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么最后就由我们「放学后茶会」的演奏来…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.87,0:18:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我有些东西想让大家听一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这张嘴比较笨拙讲不好话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.78,0:18:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以做了一首诗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  惊喜啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ときめきシュガー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大切なあなたに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,カラメルソース
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,グラニュー糖に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ブラウンシュガー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,メープル　ハチミツ　和三盆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたのために　カラメルソース
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私のハートも　カラメルソース
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ちょっぴり焦げついちゃっても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火加減で　おいしくなるの！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人心跳的砂糖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.72,0:19:01.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给重要的你涂满糖汁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:03.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,细砂糖加上红糖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,槭糖  蜂蜜  和三盆糖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.80,0:19:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了你涂满糖汁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心也涂满糖汁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使稍微有点烧焦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.35,0:19:15.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会因你的火候而变得美味！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是粉丝也到达不了澪的境界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在开始演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「放学后茶会」的新曲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.24,0:19:32.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「纯洁之心」～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来来来来来来～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.37,0:19:58.23,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭の中　想いでいっぱい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:20:01.28,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あふれそうなの　ちょっと心配
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:05.74,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,とりあえず　ヘッドホンで　ふさごう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.96,0:20:07.58,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop the music!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:10.58,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欲しいものは　欲しいって言うの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:13.77,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,したいことは　したいって言うの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.97,0:20:17.95,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だけど言えない言葉もあるの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.34,0:20:19.99,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can't stop the heartbeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:23.11,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いきなり！　チャンス到来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:26.15,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ぐうぜん同じ帰り道　Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:29.08,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふくらむ胸の風船
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:32.38,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急に足が宙に浮くの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.51,0:20:35.48,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上昇気流にのって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:39.28,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛んでいっちゃえ！　キミのもとへ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.41,0:20:41.97,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,わたしの　ぴゅあぴゅあはーと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:47.87,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受けとめてくれるなら　恐くはないの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:53.27,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この気持ちが　大気圏　越えたとき
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.42,0:20:56.43,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キミは見えなくなってた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.55,0:21:02.81,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道の向こう側　あい★ Don't mind
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.37,0:19:58.23,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑海里充满了回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:20:01.28,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要溢出来了　有点担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:05.74,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先用耳机塞住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.96,0:20:07.58,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop the music!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:10.58,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要的东西就说想要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:13.77,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的东西就说想做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.97,0:20:17.95,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也有说不出口的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.34,0:20:19.99,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can't stop the heartbeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:23.11,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然之间！ 机会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:26.15,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔走的是同一条回家的路　Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:29.08,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中的气球鼓了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:32.38,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然脚离开了地面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.51,0:20:35.48,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着上升气流而去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:39.28,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞走吧！ 飞到你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.41,0:20:41.97,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的Pure Pure Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:47.87,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能接受的话　我就不再害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:53.27,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当这份心情穿越大气圈的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.42,0:20:56.43,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就看不到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.55,0:21:02.81,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在道路的对面　I★ Don't mind
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  茄子～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.86,0:21:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后请向着这边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.61,0:21:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都太挨着澪了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想让曾我部学姐也看看这场景呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.99,0:21:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.39,0:21:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照了又怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发给曾我部学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.88,0:21:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  但是手机号码…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.61,0:21:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,号码就请学生会去调查
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:16.14,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛の言葉ちりばめた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:19.24,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌は素直でいいよね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:23.59,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なにげに口ずさんで歩こう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.86,0:21:25.33,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop the music!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:28.63,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綿菓子よりあまいメロディ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.82,0:21:31.64,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花火よりもあついリズム
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:36.03,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好きな曲は好きって言えるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:37.87,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can't stop my heartbeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.01,0:21:40.97,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不意打ち!　ピンチ到来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:43.67,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ハミング　聞かれちゃったかも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.79,0:21:47.20,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No!　はじめて　目があって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:50.21,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うれしいけど　はずかしくて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:53.29,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃げ腰なのよ　どうしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:21:56.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突っ走っちゃえ!　道ばたで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:21:59.85,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふるえてる　ぴゅあぴゅあはーと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.93,0:22:05.91,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どこまでも透明な　あの空高く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.04,0:22:08.32,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生まれたての…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:16.14,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}镶嵌了爱的话语
