Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:23.59,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}无意间哼唱着前行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.86,0:21:25.33,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}Don't stop the music!
