Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:43.67,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}似乎被听到了哼唱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.79,0:21:47.20,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}No!　头一次的目光衔接
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:50.21,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}虽然高兴　又很害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:53.29,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}马上转身跑掉了　怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:21:56.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}飞跑向前　在路边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:21:59.85,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}颤抖着的Pure Pure Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.93,0:22:05.91,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}到哪里都透明得如同那高空一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.04,0:22:08.32,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27}新生的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.56,0:21:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去买点喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.51,0:21:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又收到了份好东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.47,0:21:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬启  曾我部学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.44,0:22:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次请学姐也一定要来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.66,0:22:05.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会是一场出色的茶会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.51,0:23:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的将来要好好考虑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.38,0:23:53.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得还远着呢  太难想象了…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.22,0:23:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  你还没决定志愿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.08,0:23:58.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.69,0:24:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就那样了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.93,0:24:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  就写上自己现在最想做的怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.24,0:24:07.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己最想做的…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.59,0:24:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了！


